metadata.name: of love and hate
metadata.description:
::: 4000x4000 px png  
::: "of love and hate" depicting life of a family. the story come after my personal experience in the past when my father left us for other woman. Until one day, he come back to our life when that woman left him. love and hate - October 2022  
::: Artwork made with digital painting + digital editing. Experimenting my abstract work with glitch effect and additional layer of my previous generative shape work.
